{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Embark on an intriguing adventure, where you have been summoned by a powerful God, on a mission: to recover the sacred balls that were stolen from this God.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/ChegandoNaBolaGIF_ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1734346117\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The stolen balls.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick up the balls that are scattered across different levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are several balls of different colors to be captured.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find them, capture them and take them to the boxes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/GuardandoBolaGIF_ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1734346117\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Store the balls in the boxes, to return the balls to the God who takes care of these balls</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each box has the same color as the ball.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The boxes are a portal for the balls to reach the God.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you reach certain numbers of stored balls, something will happen.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/MostrandoPor\u00f5esGIF_ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1734346117\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unlock new levels according to how many balls were stored in the boxes.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each level has a different visual aspect.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At each level, the challenges will increase in complexity to be solved.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each level has a specific number of balls to be collected.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With each new level, the number of balls to be captured also increased.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/MostrandoPuzzlesGIF_ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1734346117\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The challenges of each level will become more difficult.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is a learning curve for each puzzle, one puzzle teaches you something about the next puzzle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some puzzles are to free access to the ball, some other puzzles are to free the exit from the level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will need to complete the puzzles to progress in the game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734346117","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734346117","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/a900c813a81190436c33c0e75498bf9b5d6e3bb8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734346117","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/a900c813a81190436c33c0e75498bf9b5d6e3bb8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734346117","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3303980,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Embark on an intriguing adventure, where you have bee